sourcesContent:
export const strategies = [
  {
    id: '1',
    title: 'Flash Trade',
    user: 'QuickTrader',
    liveTokens: 7,
    description: 'Quick in and out based on volume spikes',
    parameters: [
      { label: 'Entry Time', value: '5 minutes' },
      { label: 'Exit Time', value: '15 minutes' },
      { label: 'Volume Spike', value: '>300%' },
      { label: 'Price Action', value: 'Breakout' },
    ],
    metrics: [
      { label: 'Total Trades', value: '234' },
      { label: 'Success Rate', value: '65%' },
      { label: 'Average Return', value: '+8.3%' },
      { label: 'Best Trade', value: '+32.1%' },
    ]
  },
  {
    id: '2',
    title: 'Diamond Hands',
    user: 'CryptoPro',
    liveTokens: 3,
    description: 'Long-term hold with smart money accumulation',
    parameters: [
      { label: 'Hold Time', value: '30+ days' },
      { label: 'Smart Money', value: '3+ Wallets' },
      { label: 'Volume Trend', value: 'Increasing' },
      { label: 'Market Cap', value: '<$10M' },
    ],
    metrics: [
      { label: 'Total Trades', value: '89' },
      { label: 'Success Rate', value: '85%' },
      { label: 'Average Return', value: '+28.5%' },
      { label: 'Best Trade', value: '+156.7%' },
    ]
  },
  {
    id: '3',
    title: 'Quick Pump',
    user: 'AlphaWizard',
    liveTokens: 5,
    description: '2+ Smart Wallet Buys, Volume Spike > 200%',
    parameters: [
      { label: 'Minimum Volume', value: '$100k' },
      { label: 'Wallet Threshold', value: '2+ Smart Wallets' },
      { label: 'Volume Spike', value: '>200%' },
      { label: 'Time Window', value: '1 hour' },
    ],
    metrics: [
      { label: 'Total Trades', value: '156' },
      { label: 'Success Rate', value: '72%' },
      { label: 'Average Return', value: '+15.2%' },
      { label: 'Best Trade', value: '+42.3%' },
    ]
  }
];

export const getStrategyById = (id) => strategies.find(s => s.id === id);
